file.name: spec-template.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Voximplant demo gateway
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /specs:
    get:
      x-yc-apigateway-integration:
        type: cloud_functions
        function_id: <function-id>
        tag: $latest
        service_account: <service-account-id>
      operationId: list-specs
      summary: List specializations
  /places:
    get:
      x-yc-apigateway-integration:
        type: cloud_functions
        function_id: <function-id>
        tag: $latest
        service_account: <service-account-id>
      operationId: list-places
      summary: List places
  /dates:
    get:
      x-yc-apigateway-integration:
        type: cloud_functions
        function_id: <function-id>
        tag: $latest
        service_account: <service-account-id>
      operationId: list-dates
      parameters:
        - description: Spec id
          in: query
          name: specId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Place id
          in: query
          name: placeId
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
      summary: List dates
  /doctors:
    get:
      x-yc-apigateway-integration:
        type: cloud_functions
        function_id: <function-id>
        tag: $latest
        service_account: <service-account-id>
      operationId: list-doctors
      parameters:
        - description: Spec id
          in: query
          name: specId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Place id
          in: query
          name: placeId
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Date
          in: query
          name: date
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      summary: List doctors
  /slots:
    post:
      x-yc-apigateway-integration:
        type: cloud_functions
        function_id: <function-id>
        tag: $latest
        service_account: <service-account-id>
      operationId: search-slots
      parameters:
        - description: Client id
          in: query
          name: clientId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Spec id
          in: query
          name: specId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Place id
          in: query
          name: placeId
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Date
          in: query
          name: date
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Doctors
          in: query
          name: doctor
          required: false
          schema:
            items:
              type: string
            type: array
          style: form
        - description: Slots to be excluded
          in: query
          name: excludeSlot
          required: false
          schema:
            items:
              type: string
            type: array
          style: form
        - description: Slots to be canceled
          in: query
          name: cancelSlot
          required: false
          schema:
            items:
              type: string
            type: array
          style: form
      summary: Search for slots and prebook them
  /slots/{slotId}/ack:
    post:
      x-yc-apigateway-integration:
        type: cloud_functions
        function_id: <function-id>
        tag: $latest
        service_account: <service-account-id>
      operationId: ack-slot
      parameters:
        - description: Slot id
          in: path
          name: slotId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Client id
          in: query
          name: clientId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - description: Slots to be canceled
          in: query
          name: cancelSlot
          required: false
          schema:
            items:
              type: string
            type: array
          style: form
      summary: Reserve slot
